text: F♯ (eff-sharp or F-sharp; also known as fa dièse or fi) is the seventh semitone of the solfège. It lies a chromatic semitone above F and a diatonic semitone below G, thus being enharmonic to Sol Bémol or G (G-flat). ==Related pages== *F-sharp major *F-sharp minor Category:Musical notes
title: F♯ (musical note)
